[Salmonellosis may well have a fatal outcome, particularly in the very young and the elderly and those with immunodeficiencies, especially involving the humoral immune system. Co-existing illnesses in the fatalities were not, however, mentioned.

ProMED thanks Philip Henika for the 2nd report. Whether the fowl originated in Thailand or Malaysia or even the USA is really a moot point, since the reports strongly imply that kitchen hygiene and refrigeration were quite inadequate. - Mod.LL

